review:
Doctor is absolutely friendly and she takes perfect care regarding treatment and health as well of the patients.Actually one super cool doc whom I have never seen and also maintenance wise asking to follow simple procedures which is easy to do on a daily basis....
According to me as a patient,this doctor based on her experience and way of approaching patients ,she is highly recommended üíØüòâüëç

********* ******** **** *** ******* ********** She takes utmost care to get our problem resolved. I have done my root canal treatment with her few months back and I am very much satisfied after the treatment. 
Dr. Yamuna is also available over the phone to attend all our queries after the treatment. The clinic is also neat and clean. I would recommend Dr. Yamuna to anyone suffering from tooth ache.

Knows her job.  Confident.  Patiently deals with the issues. Briefs about the treatment process.  Well equipped.  Clean and hygienic. Enquires about the wellness  after every treatment.  Good ambience Good staff. Friendly.  Overall experience is excellent.
